channel.title: My server in the making
channel.description:
Hello everyone, i'm not sure if any of you remember me but I was here a while back with diagnostic-pk. Wasn't much of a server in fact it only had like 20 people on. But anyways, I am hoping to get back and be active on here and start a new server. This server is PI based and i'm looking for a person/people to help me make it. The source is nividia I believe so a big thanks to whoever made that for the source and client. I'm not really that good with all the java stuff and i'm basically looking for people to help me learn and to help me with the server. I haven't really came up with a name for it yet but post back to this in this format:
Java knowledge: 1/10 MSN: Would you like to help: yes/no
Thank you all of you that try to help.. And I do not know if this is in the right section I didn't really see one for it so if it is in the wrong section could a moderator please move it;)
Sincerely, Vexillum.
